Radisson Blu Resort - 3 Nights and 4 Days

Witness the true magic of Kaptai with a boat ride among the serene waters of Kaptai lake. The beauty of the Shubholong waterfall will enchant your journey through the hills. A spiritual adventure awaits you at Rajbon Bihar. Experience the cultures of Rangamati with this tour.

Places that will be covered in this tour

Shubholong Waterfall
Hanging Bridge
Polwel Park
Peda Ting Ting Restaurant
Rajbon Bihar
Shubholong waterfall (small)